<p><b>SS <i>Arlington</i></b> was a <a href="/wiki/Great_Lakes" title="Great Lakes">Great Lakes</a> <a href="/wiki/Steamship" title="Steamship">steamship</a> which was lost in <a href="/wiki/Lake_Superior" title="Lake Superior">Lake Superior</a> on May 1, 1940.</p>
<p></p>
